      <title>格兰特·沙普斯因平民面临风险而阻止英国向加沙空投援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/uk-defense-chief-grant-shapps-blocks-gaza-aid-drops-over-civilian-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，出于对平民面临风险的担忧，英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯阻止了英国向加沙地带空投援助物资，这突显了盟军在向战区运送物资方面面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/uk-defense-chief-grant-shapps-blocks-gaza-aid-drops-over-civilian-risk</guid>
