    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯威胁促使欧盟贷款部门考虑为防御提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russian-threat-spurs-eu-s-lending-arm-to-look-at-funding-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行正在考虑如何扩大对国防工业的支持，此举将有助于欧盟加强安全，应对来自俄罗斯日益增长的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russian-threat-spurs-eu-s-lending-arm-to-look-at-funding-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:51:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>种族主义争议激怒保守党，苏纳克拒绝退还捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)不顾压力，将一名商人向其保守党退还1000万英镑(1280万美元)的捐款，首相谴责这名商人过去对反对派政客发表“种族主义”言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
